      "title": "Evening Unwind",
      "description": "After returning home, Eleanor cooks a Mediterranean-inspired vegetarian dinner for her family. They talk about Clara\u2019s environmental science project and Thomas's upcoming cello recital. Later, she sinks into her armchair with a biography of Hildegard of Bingen, occasionally making margin notes for a conference paper she\u2019s planning on medieval herbal traditions. She closes her evening with twenty minutes of meditation before bed."
