      "description": "At her office filled with scholarly texts and potted mint, Eleanor prepares her lecture slides for a graduate seminar on integrative nutrition. She moves from meeting to meeting\u2014providing publication advice to a young naturopath, attending the ethics committee\u2019s review of a pilot study, and concluding the day with an impromptu discussion with colleagues about new advances in acupuncture research."
