    {
      "title": "Morning in the Garden",
      "description": "Eleanor wakes before sunrise, brewing a pot of chamomile tea while she looks out over her medicinal garden beaded with dew. She spends an hour tending to lavender and echinacea plants, noting new blooms for an upcoming clinical herbology workshop. With her garden gloves still on, she checks her research emails, responding carefully to a naturopathic student\u2019s question about designing a trial on herbal sleep aids."
